<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٩٤ - عَنْ رَجُلٍ , عَنْ أَبِي الضُّحَى , أَتَى رَجُلٌ ابْنَ عُمَرَ،<span style="color:#006d98"> فَقَالَ:</span> إِنِّي قَتَلْتُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">فَقَرَأَ عَلَيْهِ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" <span style="color:#947721">{وَمَنْ يَقْتُلْ مُؤْمِنًا مُتَعَمِّدًا فَجَزَاؤُهُ جَهَنَّمُ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[النساء: ٩٣]</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">ثُمَّ قَالَ:</span> انْظُرْ مَنْ قَتَلْتَ "<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>